    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><persName><name ref="Adroaldus">Atrualdo</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Dominicus">Dominichi</name></persName>
                        viene posto da <persName ref="#people/214" key="#Bishops"
                            >Gherardus</persName>, gratia Dei huius sancte Lucane ecclesie umilis
                            <rs key="#Bishops">episcopus</rs>, per cartula livellario nomine (…), in
                        casa et res illa in loco et finibus ubi dicitur <placeName
                            ref="#places/2102">Cassio</placeName>, pertenentes ipsius <rs
                            key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> vestro <orgName
                            ref="#juridical_persons/68" key="#Mother_churches">Sancti
                            Martini</orgName>; quas ego modo ad manus mea abere videor; casa vero
                        ipsa cum fundamento et edeficio suo, seo curte, orto, terris, vineis,
                        silvis, virgareis, pratis, pascuis, cultas res vel incultas, omnia quantum
                        ad ipsa casa est pertinentes (…) in integrum me inibi firmasti (…). Obbligo:
                        ego vel meis heredes in ipsa casa residere et abitare debeamus et tam ipsa
                        casa et res bene laborare et gubernare seo meliorare debeamus (…). Censo:
                        pro omni censum et iustitia exinde tibi vel ad successoribus tuis ad parte
                        ipsius vestro, per singulos annos, vobis vel ad misso vestro in ipso loco
                        reddere debeamus vino mundo sistaria viginti quattuor ad legitimo sistario
                        quale in ipso loco percurrit et, per omnem mense decembrio, vobis reddere
                        debeamus argentum denarios bonos expendiviles numero viginti et sex et, de
                        quinto in quinto annos, vobis reddere debeamus berbice uno annotino
                        valientes denarios tres et uno saccho; et mandato vestro venire debeamus hic
                        Luca legem et iustitiam faciendum tantum. Pena: (…) spondeo ego qui supra
                        Atrualdo una cum meis heredes conponere tibi (…) penam argentum soledos
                        viginti (…). <persName key="#Writer #Witness #Notary"><name ref="Andreas"
                                >Andreas</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> scrive due <rs
                            key="#Libellus/precaria/emphyteusis">cartulas</rs>. Actum <placeName
                            ref="#places/4" key="#Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>.</ab>
                    <ab>Sottoscrivono come <rs key="#Witness">testimoni</rs>: <persName
                            ref="#people/149" key="#Witness">Cunimundo</persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary"><name ref="Gumbertus">Gumpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Huuarnari">Vuarneri</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Willeradus">Guillerado</name></persName> filio <persName
                            key="#Witness">quondam <name ref="Osprandus">Osprandi</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Lambrandus"
                            >Lamprando</name></persName> filio <persName>quondam <name
                                ref="Lambertus">Lamperti</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Angelfredus">Anghalfridi</name></persName> filio
                            <persName>quondam <name ref="Sildifredus"
                        >Sildifridi</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
